OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRoyal Mail staff absences  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdouble levels of 2018      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Royal Mail has confirmed that absence  
OL,6, levels are double those seen in 2018   
OL,7, before the coronavirus pandemic.       
OL,9,FIt has insisted that deliveries are    
OL,10,Foperating as normal across most of the 
OL,11,Fcountry.                               
OL,13,FHowever, a source with close knowledge 
OL,14,Fof its operations has said the internal
OL,15,Fsituation is "horrific" due to sickness
OL,16,Fand increased demand in the run-up to  
OL,17,FChristmas.                             
OL,19,FThat source claimed: "It's much worse  
OL,20,Fthan a normal Christmas."              
